== Amateka ==
Uwera Dalila yashakanye n’umugabo Dirk basanzwe baba mu gihugu cy’u Bubiligi, yabwiye Radio Rwanda icyatumye yitabira iri irushanwa rya [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda#cite note-3|Nyaminga Wu Rwanda]]  ryari ribaye ku nshuro ya kabiri mu gihugu .Yagumye asobanura icyatumye ajya muri Miss Rwanda 1993 . Yavuze ko yarasanzwe arumunyamideli guhora abikora yerekana imyambaro igenzweho ikindi abobari bashinzwe ibyo bbyimideri ninabo nabo Bamujyanye mwi rushanwa rya Nyaminga wu [[Rwanda|Rwanda.]]Nyuma yaho yaje gushakana numugabo kumugabane wiburayi ari we Dirk. [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda#cite note-3|Uwera Dalila]] yaje guhishuye andi mabanga y’urugo rwe mu biganiro  yagirinye  nitangazamakuru hano mu Rwwanda  aho yahamirije abanyamakuru ko yamaze gutandukana n’umubiligi bari barashakanye,gusa yirinda kugaruka ku cyo yapfuye n’uyu wahoze ari umugabo we na cyane ko ngo ari ibintu biri hagati yabo ndetse yumva nta mpamvu n’imwe yatuma atangaza icyo bapfuye.<ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/uwera-dalila-wabaye-miss-rwanda-mu-1994-ntiyumva-neza-impamvu-adahabwa-agaciro</ref>

Uwera Dalila yavuzeko yaje gutandukanye n’umugabo bari barashakanye nyuma yo kubyarana umwana umwe, muri kiriya gihe yarafitr ubu . Mu kiganiro ni icyo kinyamakuru yavuze ko nyuma yo gutandukana n’uyu wari umugabo we yatangiye ubuzima bushya ndetse anongeraho ko yamaze kubona umusore bakundana bagiye kumarana umwaka wose bari mu rukundo ndetse bakaba biteguye kurushinga mu gihe icyo aricyo cyose baba bamaze kubyumvikana<ref>https://rushyashya.net/ntabwo-uwera-dalila-yabaye-miss-wambere-mu-rwanda-nkuko-bimaze-iminsi-byandikwa-mu-binyamakuru-kuko-uwabaye-miss-rwanda-1992-yishwe-muri-jenoside-yakorewe-abatutsi/</ref>

== Ibihembo  ==
Uwera Dalila Avugako Bahawe ikamba arabakobwa 20  avugako Bimwe muhihembo Yibuka harimo Imikufi hanyuma ibindi bakaba batarabibonye kubera bayise  bahunga  berekeza mugabane w’u [[Burayi]].<ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/uwera-dalila-wabaye-miss-rwanda-mu-1994-ntiyumva-neza-impamvu-adahabwa-agaciro</ref>

== Icyo  avuga ==
Avuga ko kuba yarmbaye ikamba rya [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda#cite note-3|Nyampinga w’u Rwanda]] wo muri 1993 abona ari agaciro gakomeye kuri we ndetse ko kugeza ubu agifite ishema ryaryo.Arongera aravugango Kuba yarabaye Nyampinga w’u [[Rwanda]] bivuga byinshi cyane.byamuhesheje agaciro byatumye amenya agaciro kiwe , byatumye akomeza kuba umwali ukwiriye u Rwanda n’ubu aracyabyitirirwa, aracyitirirwa Nyampinga w’u [[Rwanda]] akaba ari naryo shema nanubu aifite, nta nyungu akurikiranye cyane ariko agaciro gakomeye afite n’uko yahagarariye u [[Rwanda]].<ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/uwera-dalila-wabaye-miss-rwanda-mu-1994-ntiyumva-neza-impamvu-adahabwa-agaciro</ref>
